title: Help Us Study Atrial Fibrillation
body:
Join the Librexia AF Study evaluating an investigational medication to reduce the risk of atrial fibrillation (AF or AFib) complications.

Your participation may help us learn more about the study medication.

title: Living with Atrial Fibrillation (AF)?
body:
Help research an investigational AFib medication. Learn about a new clinical study.

Certain diseases and medications may impact people differently based on their age, sex, and genetic background, including race and ethnicity. We are committed to connecting potential  participants from diverse and representative groups to our trial opportunity to help ensure that investigational medications are generally safe and effective (or that the benefits outweigh the risks) for the populations impacted.
